**Problem:** Sequential queries ‚Äî worst case is 3 round-trips. With unique usernames across tables, `Promise.all` would cut latency to 1 round-trip.

**Fix:**
```typescript
const [admin, guru, siswa] = await Promise.all([
  prisma.admin.findUnique({ where: { username } }),
  prisma.guru.findUnique({ where: { username } }),
  prisma.siswa.findUnique({ where: { username } }),
]);
// Then check password on whichever matched
